---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Avakkai Studio">
  <section class="bg-brand-dark min-h-screen py-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-brand-primary text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-body font-bold mb-4">
          Legal
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white font-display leading-tight mb-4">
          Privacy <span class="text-brand-secondary italic font-normal">Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-mono">Last updated: July 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-headings:font-display prose-headings:text-white prose-p:text-zinc-300 prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-strong:text-white max-w-none">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          Avakkai Studio collects information you provide directly, such as when you:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact us via email or phone</li>
          <li>Submit a project inquiry</li>
          <li>Sign up for our newsletter</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          This may include your name, email address, phone number, and company name.
        </p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
          <li>Provide information about our services</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          <li>Send marketing communications (with your consent)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Rectify inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may use third-party services such as:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>YouTube:</strong> For embedding project videos</li>
          <li><strong>Email Services:</strong> For communication</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> To understand website usage (if applicable)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These services have their own privacy policies and we encourage you to review them.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> reach@avakkai.studio</li>
          <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +91 96111 04445</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>